extends layout

block content
  h1= 'Hanabi'
  p find the code repository here: 
    a.text(href='https://github.com/xonnie/hanabi') https://github.com/xonnie/hanabi
  h3 A cooperative card game for 2 to 5 players. 
  p you can register with any name without password, and start a game with anyone, also if they didn't register yet.
  p rules are simple: try to reach a score as close to 25 as possible. But beware, if all lives are lost, you lose. 
  p Each player can only see the cards of the other player(s). 
  div
    form(action='/register' method='get')
      input(type='submit' value='register')
      label(for="user_id") as
      input(type="text" name="name" id="user_id")
